text: Erik Duvander (born 23 February 1962) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:American male equestrians Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chicago
